articles.description: Cortez Edwards scored 12 points, grabbed 10 rebounds, distributed six assists and had five steals and Southern Mississippi cruised to 72-54 win over Charlotte on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Edwards leads Southern Mississippi past Charlotte 72-54

articles.description: The No. 2 Cavaliers force overtime with a pair of late buckets from Ty Jerome, but in the extra session, the Hokies' Kerry Blackshear Jr. scores an and-1 with under 10 seconds remaining for a 61-60 victory.
articles.headline: Virginia Tech takes down No. 2 Virginia in OT

images.caption: The No. 2 Cavaliers force overtime with a pair of late buckets from Ty Jerome, but in the extra session, the Hokies' Kerry Blackshear Jr. scores an and-1 with under 10 seconds remaining for a 61-60 victory.
images.name: Virginia Tech takes down No. 2 Virginia in OT

articles.description: Macio Teague hits a game-winning shot for UNC Asheville with just over four seconds remaining, sending the broadcaster into a frenzy.
articles.headline: UNC Asheville announcer goes wild after game winner

articles.description: Kevin Hervey had 33 points, eight rebounds and four blocks as UT Arlington held on to beat Texas State 70-68 in overtime on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Hervey has 33 points, UT Arlington holds off Texas St. in OT

articles.description: Ivy Smith Jr. scored the final seven points and Grambling held off Prairie View A&M, 90-85 on Saturday night to win their ninth straight game and move into a first-place tie in the Southwestern Conference.
articles.headline: Grambling beats Prairie View 90-85, moves into 1st-place tie
